    T - type of contained events
    public class ResultEvent<T extends DESEvent>
extends java.lang.Object
    ResultEvents is a container of events and offers helper methods to inspect the result. This eases the checking of the contract.

      • areMany

        public boolean areMany()
        Returns true iff more than one intermediate events are specified in this result event. It always returns false iff either isOne() or isEmpty() are true.

      • isOne

        public boolean isOne()
        Returns true iff there is exactly one immediate event specified in this result event. It always returns false iff either areMany() or isEmpty() are true.

      • isEmpty

        public boolean isEmpty()
        Returns true iff there are no immediate event specified in this result event. It always returns false iff either isOne() or areMany() are true.
